incorporation of more complex halogen-containing molecules such as organohalogens
into planet-forming regions is uncertain. Here we report the interstellar detection
of two isotopologues of the organohalogen CH3Cl and put some constraints on CH3F
in the gas surrounding the low-mass protostar IRAS 16293â€“2422, using the Atacama
