polynomial expansions. The average accuracy of the line parameters obtained in this
work has been estimated to be between 0.1 x 10(-3) and 1 x 10(-3) cm(-1) for line
positions, between 2\% and 5\% for line intensities and between 5\% and 10\% for
self-broadening coefficients depending on the transitions. (C) 2013 Elsevier Ltd.
All rights reserved.},
Doi = {10.1016/j.jqsrt.2013.02.002}
}


@Article{13aBrJaLa.CH3Cl,
Author = {Bray, C. and Jacquemart, D. and Lacome, N.},
Title = {{Temperature dependence for self- and {N}$_{2}$-broadening coefficients of {CH}$_{3}${Cl}}},
